data.description: A beautiful rare waterfront 2bedroom/2bath JUNIOR PENTHOUSE SUITE awaits you - offering breathtaking panoramic views of the ocean, the harbor, Catalina Island, Queen Mary, Carnival cruise ships, July 4th and New Years Eve fireworks, close to the Jazz, Country and Reggae concerts. Plus an added bonus - The Iconic Long Beach Grand Prix and Formula Drift overlooking Turns 9,10 and 11 Vroom Vroom!!! Take in these beautiful views from your living room, both bedrooms and private open balcony. Your castle in the sky has high 10 foot ceilings with crown molding, tall windows, and updated baths and kitchen are just a few of its special features. Renovations include custom cabinetry and quartz counters in both baths and the kitchen. Italian porcelain flooring with the classic European harlequin pattern throughout the open floor plan. Appliances are high-end and built-in: a gourmet Thermador easy-clean glass cook top, very quiet dishwasher, stainless steel convection oven and microwave. In both baths, custom shower stalls are easy-clean solid-surfaces from floor to ceiling, with frameless glass doors and no grout lines! The main bath also has a separate oversized tub. Deeded with the property are two side-by-side garage spaces and the unit comes with passes to the building for guests to watch the Grand Prix live from the balcony!     The building, the prestigious HarborPlace Tower, is in the center of the new growth of the vibrant downtown Long Beach. A Walkers Paradise score of 93 means you are within walking distance to the beach, marina, great restaurants like the 555 Club and a variety of bars, coffee shops, the Convention Center, the Pike, the Aquarium of the Pacific, Pine Ave, Shoreline Village, major hotels such as the Westin, public transportation, Vons and The Performing Arts Center. HPT features a modern lobby with 24 hour security guard on duty, package concierge, resort style pool with spa, gym, sauna, ping pong table, meeting room, BBQ’s (coming soon), Promenade deck and 80 guest parking spaces and its very close to easy freeway access. If you are looking for luxury resort style living, a second home or investment this is the place for you - Welcome Home!
